<emphasis id="CFF6EAA3FFE7FFB2FF3AFA20FEF1FA2A" box="[200,339,1432,1458]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="187">A. tenuifolia</emphasis>
Lin &amp; Yang
</taxonomicName>
in 
<bibRefCitation id="99134B40FFE7FFB2FDF0FA21FCAFFA2A" author="Meng, T. &amp; Yang, J. C. &amp; Tang, W. X. &amp; Pan, B. &amp; Lin, C. R." box="[514,781,1432,1459]" pageId="4" pageNumber="187" pagination="289 - 293" refId="ref4268" refString="Meng, T., Yang, J. C., Tang, W. X., Pan, B. &amp; Lin, C. R. (2014) Aspidistra tenuifolia (Asparagaceae), a new species from China. Phytotaxa 161: 289 - 293. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 161.4.4" type="journal article" year="2014">
